data.description: FULLY RENOVATED-Quiet All Brick Townhome Community in the Raintree Country Club Area of Charlotte with 43 homes nestled within acres of woods with common areas for strolling or walking your dog.  This home has been beautifully updated with New Kitchen (White Quiet-Close Cabinets, New SS Appliances, Tile Flooring, Quartz countertops), New LVP Flooring throughout, new blinds, tiled primary shower with niche, New vanities with fogless mirrors and quartz countertops, closet systems for organizing, New wood tread stairs. All appliances will remain to include washer and dryer.  Sidewalk to shopping at the Arboretum Area. Just a few miles to the restaurants and retail of Waverly, Rea Farms, Promenade on Providence, Stonecrest, and Providence Commons, groceries nearby-Whole Foods (2.4mi), Fresh Market (1.8mi), Trader Joes (2mi) and the new planned IKEA. Raintree Country Club is a walk away for golf, swimming and sports. Membership is a separate fee. **Option to purchase fully furnished**
